OL,4,CRalph Lauren apologises over 'cultural
OL,5,Cappropriation'
OL,6, Ralph Lauren has apologised for selling
OL,7, an item which allegedly copied Mexican
OL,8, indigenous designs.
OL,10,FThe US fashion chain was accused of
OL,11,F"plagiarism" by the wife of the
OL,12,Fcountry's president, Beatriz Gutierrez,
OL,13,Fas well as a culture minister.
OL,15,FMexico has aimed similar complaints at
OL,16,Fother big brands in recent years.
OL,18,FRalph Lauren said it was "surprised" to
OL,19,Fsee the garment in question still on
OL,20,Fsale, having issued a "stern directive"
OL,21,Fmonths previously to remove it.
